{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Privacy Policy - Hütte9{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
  <div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>

        <div class="legal-content">
          <h2>1. General</h2>
          <p>
            This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you visit our website and use our services.
          </p>

          <h2>2. Data Controller</h2>
          <p>
            The data controller under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) is:<br />
            <strong>Hütte9</strong><br />
            [Your Address]<br />
            [Your Email Address]<br />
            [Your Phone Number]
          </p>

          <h2>3. Collection and Processing of Personal Data</h2>
          <p>
            We collect the following categories of personal data:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Contact data:</strong> Name, email address, phone number</li>
            <li><strong>Booking data:</strong> Arrival and departure date, number of persons</li>
            <li><strong>Special requests:</strong> Optional message with special wishes</li>
            <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP address, browser information, timestamp</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
          <p>
            The processing of your personal data is based on your consent (Art. 6 para. 1 lit. a GDPR). You can withdraw your consent at any time without affecting the lawfulness of processing before withdrawal.
          </p>

          <h2>5. Purposes of Data Processing</h2>
          <p>
            We process your data for the following purposes:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Processing your booking request</li>
            <li>Sending confirmation emails</li>
            <li>Communication with you regarding your booking</li>
            <li>Improving our services</li>
            <li>Compliance with legal obligations</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>6. Sharing with Third Parties</h2>
          <p>
            We do not share your personal data with third parties unless it is required to fulfill our contracts or if we are legally obligated to do so.
          </p>

          <h2>7. Data Retention Period</h2>
          <p>
            Your data will only be stored for as long as it is required to fulfill the contract. After completion of the booking, your data will be deleted after a maximum of 3 years, unless legal retention obligations apply.
          </p>

          <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>
            You have the following rights regarding your personal data:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Right to access (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Right to rectification (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Right to erasure (Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Right to restrict processing (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Right to data portability (Art. 20 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Right to object (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>9. Data Security</h2>
          <p>
            We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, loss, or destruction.
          </p>

          <h2>10. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about this privacy policy or your rights, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@huette9.de<br />
            <strong>Address:</strong> [Your Address]
          </p>

          <h2>11. Right to Complain</h2>
          <p>
            You have the right to file a complaint with a data protection authority if you believe that the processing of your personal data violates the GDPR.
          </p>

          <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
            <small>This privacy policy is updated regularly. Last updated: November 2025</small>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4">
          <a href="{{ path('app_home') }}" class="btn btn-outline-primary">{{ 'Back to Home'|trans }}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <style>
    .legal-content h2 { margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }

    .legal-content p { line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    .legal-content ul { margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

    .legal-content ul li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.8; }
  </style>
{% endblock %}
